    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[0]'
      value: 'You! A good wizard, finally! '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[1]'
      value: How lucky am I that you would travel to my realm out of coincidence.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[2]'
      value: This land scarcely receives travelers.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[3]'
      value: " Actually\u2026I don't know that we have ever received\u2026 "
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[4]'
      value: "Well it has been a while.. forever\u2026since I have seen one\u2026heh."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[5]'
      value: "Anyhow! You may be able to help me if it wouldn\u2019t be too much
        trouble."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[6]'
      value: As you can see, I am trapped.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[7]'
      value: The Evil Wizard, the menace that he is...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[8]'
      value: ripped my elemental children from their dwellings and...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[9]'
      value: scattered them across the land.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
