    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[10]'
      value: In most cases, I would be there to help my offspring and pulverize the
        demon but...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[11]'
      value: he trapped me in this  before his assault, and I simply cannot pry myself
        free.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[12]'
      value: I need you-or I need your help rather.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[13]'
      value: 'My children act like small babies, they cannot sustain themselves without
        my guidance. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[14]'
      value: So please, my good wizard.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 9003078385388726310, guid: 3c974c0399c04804ea7ea5d1ff402c96, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'DialogLines.Array.data[15]'
      value: Find my babes and help them, and free me from this horrible prison.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
